description: This class focuses on teaching the fundamental techniques and principles of karate. Students will learn basic stances, punches, kicks, and blocks while developing strength, flexibility, and coordination.

Designed specifically for women, this class focuses on practical self-defense techniques, situational awareness, and assertiveness training. Gain confidence and learn how to protect yourself in various scenarios.

This class focuses on the art of sparring and controlled combat. Students will practice partner drills, timing, distance control, and strategy to enhance their competitive skills in a safe and controlled environment.

An engaging and fun-filled class for children, where they will learn basic karate skills, coordination exercises, and self-discipline. Our experienced instructors ensure a safe and enjoyable environment for all kids.
Experience the flowing movements and meditation of Tai Chi in this introductory class. Suitable for all ages and fitness levels, Tai Chi promotes relaxation, balance, and inner peace.
Take your karate skills to the next level with this advanced class. Students will learn intricate combinations, advanced forms, and specialized techniques to enhance their martial arts proficiency.
